*** MemoServ Help - Command: SET NOTIFY ***
Lets you decide when you will be notified about new memos.
 
Syntax:
/ms SET NOTIFY option
 
Available options:
 
    ON     -   You will be notified of memos when you log on, 
                 and when they are sent to you.
    LOGON  -   You will only be notified of memos when you log on.
    NEW    -   You will only be notified of memos when they are sent to you.
    OFF    -   You will not receive any notification of memos.
 
Examples:
/ms SET NOTIFY LOGON
/ms SET NOTIFY OFF
 
Type /join #IRCHelp for more information.
*** End of Help ***